This token is granted if you've attempted to gift the LEGO Pass to a friend, but they purchased it while you were in the middle of the gifting process.

You may use this token to send the LEGO Pass as a gift to another friend. If left unused, it will be refunded in the form of V-Bucks at the end of the current Season.
